snippet.title: Crystal - Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Square is the new shape that comes to Crystal, everything seems to be normal...

Now you can follow, see more information and add Crystal to your wishlist on Steam! 
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1592270/Crystal/
Game Jolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/crystal/561605

Welcome to Crystal a world where creativity and harmony have no limits
Square wants to get to the other side of the face but for that he has to go through different puzzles and tests that come across him

#crystalgame
